OL,3,CVideo shows 'brave' US high school
OL,4,Cprincipal tackling armed man in school
OL,6,FThe moment Kirk Moore tackled the
OL,7,Fshooter
OL,9,FA new video shows the moment a
OL,10,Fheadteacher of an Oklahoma high school
OL,11,Fwas shot in the leg as he tackled an
OL,12,Farmed man.
OL,14,FSecurity camera video from inside the
OL,15,FPauls Valley High School in Oklahoma
OL,16,Fshowed the suspect, former student
OL,17,FVictor Hawkins, enter the school
OL,18,Fshortly before 2.20pm on April 8 with
OL,19,Fa firearm.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776280294
OL,3,CVideo shows 'brave' US high school
OL,4,Cprincipal tackling armed man in school
OL,6,FHawkins, 20, appeared to point and
OL,7,Ffire a gun before slowly walking into
OL,8,Fthe lobby.
OL,10,FAs Hawkins points the gun at someone
OL,11,Fsitting on a bench in the lobby,
OL,12,Fprincipal Kirk Moore is seen coming
OL,13,Fout of a closed door and tackling the
OL,14,Fformer student onto the ground.
OL,16,FAt one point, the gun was pointed
OL,17,Fdirectly at Moore's head before it was
OL,18,Ftackled out of his hands and kicked
OL,19,Faway by bystanders.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776280294
OL,3,CVideo shows 'brave' US high school
OL,4,Cprincipal tackling armed man in school
OL,6,FAt some point during the incident,
OL,7,FMoore was shot in the leg. He was
OL,8,Fflown to OU Health in Oklahoma City,
OL,9,Fwhere he was treated and released a
OL,10,Ffew days later.
OL,12,FMoore, who is recovering at home, has
OL,13,Fsince expressed gratitude for "an
OL,14,Foutpouring of love and support".
OL,16,FIn a statement, he credited the
OL,17,Ftraining that many educators in the US
OL,18,Fmust undertake to prepare for school
OL,19,Fshootings for his quick reaction.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776280294
OL,3,CVideo shows 'brave' US high school
OL,4,Cprincipal tackling armed man in school
OL,6,F"Like so many educators around the
OL,7,Fcountry, we prepare for these events
OL,8,Fthrough training and careful
OL,9,Fassessment of the threats," he said.
OL,11,F"I am grateful that my instincts and
OL,12,Ftraining, as well as God's hand, were
OL,13,Favailable to me."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776280294
OL,3,CVideo shows 'brave' US high school
OL,4,Cprincipal tackling armed man in school
OL,6,FOklahoma Governor Kevin Stitt praised
OL,7,FMoore, writing on X: "Principal Moore
OL,8,Facted bravely to protect students'
OL,9,Flives. Sarah and I are praying for his
OL,10,Fquick recovery. I'm thankful for the
OL,11,Fswift response from law enforcement
OL,12,Fand school staff, and I'm grateful no
OL,13,Fstudents were harmed."
OL,15,FHawkins has been charged with two
OL,16,Fcounts of pointing a firearm, one
OL,17,Fcount of shooting with intent to kill,
OL,18,Fand two counts of unlawful carry.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
