PN,31206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776280294
OL,3,CVideo shows 'brave' US high school
OL,4,Cprincipal tackling armed man in school
OL,6,FCourt documents state that Hawkins
OL,7,Fintended to commit a mass shooting at
OL,8,Fthe school and admitted that he was
OL,9,Finfluenced by the Columbine school
OL,10,Fshooting.
OL,12,FDuring an arraignment on Wednesday,
OL,13,FHawkins told a judge he had every
OL,14,Fintention of going inside the school
OL,15,Fto shoot students, faculty, and then
OL,16,Fhimself.
OL,18,FHawkins is expected back in court on
OL,19,FMay 8.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
